        {
          "reviewTitle": "My New Go To Foundation!",
          "reviewText": "I love this powder foundation! It's my new go to! A Google search said this brand is PFAS free which is what I was looking for. I like keeping my makeup very simple at age 70. I like one step foundations in a compact. Since I haven't used this brand before I wasn't sure what color to order. There are many options on the MAC website but I only saw 3 options on Amazon. I ordered NW25. It's perfect! (I'm Scots-Irish fair with a bit of ruddiness in my cheeks.) It has good coverage but you can't tell I have makeup on. It comes in a nice compact with a sponge type applicator. It arrived in perfect condition.",
